{"TopicId":196180,"ForumId":20,"TopicTitle":"Is there a mod that automatically refuels your craft once it enters the KSC compound?","CreatedByName":"RandomKerbal","CreatedById":206026,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-08-08T05:03:30Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"RandomKerbal","CreatedById":206026,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-08-08T05:03:30Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI got this idea from here:\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Ca href=\u0022https://www.simpleplanes.com/Mods/View/855080/Fueling\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003Ehttps://www.simpleplanes.com/Mods/View/855080/Fueling\u003C/a\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222020-08-09T05:10:05Z\u0022 title=\u002208/09/2020 05:10  AM\u0022 data-short=\u00223 yr\u0022\u003EAugust 9, 2020\u003C/time\u003E by RandomKerbal\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Miguelsgamingch","CreatedById":201607,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-08-08T05:28:23Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHm. I Dont think so.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"DeadJohn","CreatedById":201293,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-08-08T05:35:38Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYou can use Hyperedit to fake it: refuel whenever you meet whatever criteria you imagine.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"RandomKerbal","CreatedById":206026,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-08-08T05:37:25Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223834046\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022196180\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221596864938\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022201293\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022DeadJohn\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n1 minute ago, DeadJohn said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYou can use Hyperedit to fake it: refuel whenever you meet whatever criteria you imagine.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIt\u0027s not realistic.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"severedsolo","CreatedById":80345,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-08-08T06:37:22Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223834047\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022196180\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221596865045\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022206026\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022RandomKerbal\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n59 minutes ago, RandomKerbal said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIt\u0027s not realistic.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAs far as I know there isn\u0027t, but if you were looking for a \u0022my first mod\u0022 project, this would be a super simple thing to code.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"SpaceCarmelo","CreatedById":194212,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-08-08T06:43:49Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nmmh for rockets you can use Modular Launchpad, you have some objects like Fuel Arm that actually refuels your tank when activated. You can write a Kos script for that if you like roleplay. Like in real life, you can load your rocket with no fuel and wait for the refueling before launch. If you wished to land with an airplane and refuel there, well you can make a refueling vehicle and script it to go near your aircraft when landed, then use some \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Kerbal Attachment System (mod)\u0022\u003EKAS\u003C/abbr\u003E joint objects to attach your plane to the refueling truck\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222020-08-08T06:44:28Z\u0022 title=\u002208/08/2020 06:44  AM\u0022 data-short=\u00223 yr\u0022\u003EAugust 8, 2020\u003C/time\u003E by SpaceCarmelo\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003Cbr\u003Ecorrection\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Miguelsgamingch","CreatedById":201607,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-08-08T08:03:12Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nMaking a mod for it will be amazing.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"RandomKerbal","CreatedById":206026,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-08-08T13:23:16Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223834095\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022196180\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221596873792\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022201607\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022miguelsgamingch\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n5 hours ago, miguelsgamingch said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nMaking a mod for it will be amazing.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYeah, I know, I don\u0027t even know how to code a plugin.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"DeadJohn","CreatedById":201293,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-08-08T17:53:51Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223834047\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022196180\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221596865045\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022206026\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022RandomKerbal\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n12 hours ago, RandomKerbal said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIt\u0027s not realistic.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n... in a game with little green astronauts \u003Cimg alt=\u0022;)\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_wink.gif\u0022 title=\u0022;)\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIf Hyperedit is too easy, use \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Kerbal Inventory System (mod)\u0022\u003EKIS\u003C/abbr\u003E/\u003Cabbr title=\u0022Kerbal Attachment System (mod)\u0022\u003EKAS\u003C/abbr\u003E with a fuel truck that you build from rover parts. There are mods for ground trucks.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"RandomKerbal","CreatedById":206026,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-08-08T18:18:33Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223834336\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022196180\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221596909231\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022201293\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022DeadJohn\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n24 minutes ago, DeadJohn said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n... in a game with little green astronauts \u003Cimg alt=\u0022;)\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_wink.gif\u0022 title=\u0022;)\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIf Hyperedit is too easy, use \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Kerbal Inventory System (mod)\u0022\u003EKIS\u003C/abbr\u003E/\u003Cabbr title=\u0022Kerbal Attachment System (mod)\u0022\u003EKAS\u003C/abbr\u003E with a fuel truck that you build from rover parts. There are mods for ground trucks.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nSometimes you can\u0027t drive a stock 100\u002B parts truck to a 500\u002B parts \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Single Stage to Orbit\u0022\u003ESSTO\u003C/abbr\u003E, with some other stuffs scattered around, and a walking kerbal, can you?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222020-08-08T18:19:08Z\u0022 title=\u002208/08/2020 06:19  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00223 yr\u0022\u003EAugust 8, 2020\u003C/time\u003E by RandomKerbal\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Lewie","CreatedById":203745,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-08-08T20:14:32Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223834355\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022196180\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221596910713\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022206026\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022RandomKerbal\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n1 hour ago, RandomKerbal said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nSometimes you can\u0027t drive a stock 100\u002B parts truck to a 500\u002B parts \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Single Stage to Orbit\u0022\u003ESSTO\u003C/abbr\u003E, with some other stuffs scattered around, and a walking kerbal, can you?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWell...you CAN but the kraken nor your computer won\u2019t\u00A0like that....\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222020-08-08T20:15:00Z\u0022 title=\u002208/08/2020 08:15  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00223 yr\u0022\u003EAugust 8, 2020\u003C/time\u003E by Lewie\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"linuxgurugamer","CreatedById":129964,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-08-08T21:37:49Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223834355\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022196180\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221596910713\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022206026\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022RandomKerbal\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n3 hours ago, RandomKerbal said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nSometimes you can\u0027t drive a stock 100\u002B parts truck to a 500\u002B parts \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Single Stage to Orbit\u0022\u003ESSTO\u003C/abbr\u003E, with some other stuffs scattered around, and a walking kerbal, can you?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYou don\u0027t need a 100\u002B part truck to carry a tank.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Gargamel","CreatedById":64714,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-08-09T19:37:17Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223834047\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022196180\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221596865045\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022206026\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022RandomKerbal\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\nOn 8/8/2020 at 1:37 AM, RandomKerbal said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIt\u0027s not realistic.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI don\u0027t see the problem with this.\u00A0\u00A0 I park my craft on the pad, and I know in the \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Vehicle Assembly Building\u0022\u003EVAB\u003C/abbr\u003E the support vehicles are all automated, so I go grab a drink from the fridge, come back, time warp a bit if I really want to add the time it takes to refuel something, and then refuel the vessel via hyper edit.\u00A0\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI would be more annoyed with a mod that forces some time delay to the refueling if it occurs during a gameplay that I really don\u0027t want it.\u00A0\u00A0 Options are options, but it\u0027s more unrealistic to go changing options during a game.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223834491\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022196180\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221596922669\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022129964\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022linuxgurugamer\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n21 hours ago, linuxgurugamer said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYou don\u0027t need a 100\u002B part truck to carry a tank.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThis.\u00A0\u00A0 You can get by with a dozen or so part vehicle.\u00A0 Just use the tank itself as the chassis, slap a cuppola on the front, some wheels, fuel cells, and batteries, and you\u0027re good to go!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nBut then comes the question..... how do you fuel the fuel truck?\u00A0\u00A0 You can despawn it and respawn it, but if you\u0027re trying to simulate an active spaceport, this nerfs the realism just as much as despawning and respawning the original craft.\u00A0\u00A0 Might as well use hyperedit.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nNow if we are writing a mod to do this, I would say limit it to a few places, in front of the \u003Cabbr title=\u0022SpacePlane Hangar\u0022\u003ESPH\u003C/abbr\u003E, and on top of the \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Vehicle Assembly Building\u0022\u003EVAB\u003C/abbr\u003E, and maybe a couple others.\u00A0\u00A0 When you are parked in these locations, a window pops up asking if you want to refuel, and what resources (I might not want to add Ore or something like that).\u00A0\u00A0\u00A0 But until that mod is made, your best bet is Hyperedit.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"linuxgurugamer","CreatedById":129964,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-08-09T19:47:54Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIf I were to write this (I\u0027m\u00A0 not), I\u0027d make a large fuel tank which can be transported and placed down, it would then slowly expand over time to full size.\u00A0 It would hold a finite amount of fuel.\u00A0 \u00A0Anything within a certain distance could be refueled, after which the tank will either fill by itself (if at a facility) or could be refueled by an \u003Cabbr title=\u0022In-Situ Resource Utilization\u0022\u003EISRU\u003C/abbr\u003E and Ore.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"theJesuit","CreatedById":122369,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-08-09T21:04:02Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nKerbal Konstructs used to do this?\u00A0 Not sure if it still does.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"RandomKerbal","CreatedById":206026,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-08-10T10:27:24Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223835010\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022196180\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221597001837\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002264714\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Gargamel\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n14 hours ago, Gargamel said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223834491\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022196180\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221596922669\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022129964\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022linuxgurugamer\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\nOn 8/9/2020 at 5:37 AM, linuxgurugamer said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYou don\u0027t need a 100\u002B part truck to carry a tank.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThis.\u00A0\u00A0 You can get by with a dozen or so part vehicle.\u00A0 Just use the tank itself as the chassis, slap a cuppola on the front, some wheels, fuel cells, and batteries, and you\u0027re good to go!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYeah, I know...\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"JadeOfMaar","CreatedById":167617,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-08-10T21:05:26Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/206026-randomkerbal/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u0022206026\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/206026-randomkerbal/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@RandomKerbal\u003C/a\u003E \u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/129964-linuxgurugamer/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u0022129964\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/129964-linuxgurugamer/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@linuxgurugamer\u003C/a\u003E That mod exists. Note: it does not subtract funds when it operates. You get free fuel.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Ciframe allowfullscreen=\u0022\u0022 data-controller=\u0022core.front.core.autosizeiframe\u0022 data-embedauthorid=\u002245759\u0022 data-embedcontent=\u0022\u0022 data-embedid=\u0022embed2425560251\u0022 scrolling=\u0022no\u0022 src=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/topic/147536-141-simplerefuel-03/\u0026amp;do=embed\u0022 style=\u0022height:214px;max-width:502px;\u0022\u003E\u003C/iframe\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/122369-thejesuit/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u0022122369\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/122369-thejesuit/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@theJesuit\u003C/a\u003E KK allows you to have fuel tank statics so you can buy and sell fuel for the active vessel in flight. Rather than have a fuel truck, drive your craft into range of this static (300m) or land it within range if it can\u0027t taxi around, and click in the fuel UI (like going to a gas station IRL). \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Kerbal Space Center\u0022\u003EKSC\u003C/abbr\u003E Extended and JNSQ have these at their space centers.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223835010\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022196180\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221597001837\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002264714\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Gargamel\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\nOn 8/9/2020 at 3:37 PM, Gargamel said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nBut then comes the question..... how do you fuel the fuel truck?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAssuming you\u0027re willing and able to install KK and setup a fuel depot, that\u0027s how you fuel the fuel truck.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222020-08-10T21:16:36Z\u0022 title=\u002208/10/2020 09:16  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00223 yr\u0022\u003EAugust 10, 2020\u003C/time\u003E by JadeOfMaar\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"jimmymcgoochie","CreatedById":199902,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-08-15T20:26:56Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nA slightly different suggestion to what has been said before:\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nSimple Logistics allows resources to be shifted between nearby landed vessels. Just launch a new tanker vehicle full of fuel, park it vaguely near your rocket and plug it in to the SL network, use SL UI to transfer fuel to the rocket. No additional parts required as SL works with pretty much every part with a control point and no need to connect the two together with anything so it reduces the kraken factor. It can also be done anywhere you like including other planets so it\u0027s beneficial for mining fuel on other planets/moons; I used it to mine fuel on Ike and refuel a Duna/Ike interplanetary ship by leaving the mining ship on Ike permanently and using drone fuel ships to carry the fuel to the main ship.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222020-08-15T20:27:04Z\u0022 title=\u002208/15/2020 08:27  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00223 yr\u0022\u003EAugust 15, 2020\u003C/time\u003E by jimmymcgoochie\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"}]}